Maximize:

	Use the Maximize button to expand the dimensions of the
	window or icon at the pointer location to a larger format
	(specified by the application).

Press-drag-release mode:

	Drag SELECT or MENU onto the button and release SELECT to
	increase the size of the window or icon at the pointer location.

Stay-up mode:

	Click SELECT or MENU on the window menu button to post the
	window menu. Move the pointer over the button, and click
	SELECT to expand the window to the maximium size allowed
	by the application.
